Rules for Choosing a Layout for a Device

CRM Analytics chooses the optimal layout when displaying the dashboard on a device, using the device properties specified for each layout.

The rules for determining which layout to use are:
- A layout is eligible if the device meets all its device properties.
- If multiple layouts are eligible, the one with the most device properties set is used. If tied, the most recently defined layout is used.
- If no layouts are eligible, the first defined layout is used.
title: Choosing Dashboard Layouts in CRM Analytics
